<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="K_6142" type="Brief"><teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>Clemente Maraini an Alfred Escher, Rom, Montag, 23. Februar 1874</title></titleStmt><publicationStmt><p>Digitale Briefedition Alfred Escher, Zürich: Alfred Escher-Stiftung.</p></publicationStmt><sourceDesc><msDesc><msIdentifier><institution>SBB Historic</institution><idno>VGB_GB_SBBGB01_006</idno></msIdentifier></msDesc><bibl type="printed"/></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><textClass><keywords scheme="http://briefedition.alfred-escher.ch/keywords"><term>Gotthardbahn-Gesellschaft (GB)</term></keywords></textClass><correspDesc><correspAction type="sent"><persName key="Maraini Clemente" type="addressee">Clemente Maraini</persName><persName key="Escher (vom Glas) Alfred" type="sender">Alfred Escher</persName><placeName>Rom</placeName><date when="1874-02-23">23. Februar 1874</date></correspAction><correspContext><ref type="previous" target="B8137"/><ref type="next" target="B2655"/><ref type="next-in-corresp" target="B6144"/><ref type="previous-in-corresp" target="B5747"/></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><front>
      <div type="dateline">
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_6142_p1"> <note type="addendum" xml:id="K_6142_c0">Nachträglicher Stempel oben rechts mit von dritter Hand eingetragener Nummer: <orig>Gotthardbahn | <date when="1874-03-07">7 <choice><abbr>MAR.</abbr><expan>MÄRZ</expan></choice> 1874</date>. | <choice><abbr>N<hi rend="sup">o</hi> </abbr><expan>Numero (Nummer)</expan></choice> 1067.</orig> – 
              Nachträgliche Inhaltsangabe oben links von dritter Hand:  <orig>Ergänzung <choice><abbr>betr.</abbr><expan>betreffend</expan></choice> d. Honorar <choice><abbr>v.</abbr><expan>von</expan></choice> 6000 <choice><abbr>fr</abbr><expan>franken / francs / franchi</expan></choice> pro 1873. | <choice><abbr>Präs.</abbr><expan>Präsidium</expan></choice> </orig> –
              Nachträgliche Notiz unten in der Mitte von dritter Hand: <orig><choice><abbr>Prot.</abbr><expan>Protokoll</expan></choice> <date when="1874-02-26">26. II. 74</date>. <choice><abbr>N.</abbr><expan>Nummer</expan></choice> 331.</orig> </note> <lb xml:id="p1-l1"/>
          <placeName key="Rom (I)">Rome</placeName>
          <date when="1874-02-23">23 Février 1874</date>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div type="opener">
        <p rend="left" xml:id="K_6142_p2"><lb xml:id="p1-l2"/>Honoré Monsieur,</p>
      </div>
    </front><body>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_6142_p3"><lb xml:id="p1-l3"/>Je suis obbligé<note type="transcript">sic!</note> de vous signaler
<lb xml:id="p1-l4"/>une omission dans ma <rs>lettre<ref type="letter" target="K_5747"/></rs> <lb xml:id="p1-l5"/>du <date when="1874-02-21">21 <choice><abbr>ct.</abbr><expan>courant (laufenden [Monats])</expan></choice> </date> adressée à la Direction du
<lb xml:id="p1-l6"/>chemin de fer du Gothard.
      </p>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_6142_p4"><lb xml:id="p1-l7"/>Dans la première période
      <lb xml:id="p1-l8"/>de ma lettre, pressé par le
      <lb xml:id="p1-l9"/>temps, j'ai oublié d'écrire
      <lb xml:id="p1-l10"/>le chifre<note type="transcript">sic</note> de <choice><abbr>F<hi rend="sup">rs</hi> </abbr><expan>Francs (Franken)</expan></choice> 6,000. Je vous
      <lb xml:id="p1-l11"/>prie, honoré Monsieur, de vouloir
        <lb xml:id="p1-l12"/>bien faire reparér par <persName key="Schweizer Friedrich">votre
      <lb xml:id="p1-l13"/>secretaire</persName> cette omission, avant
      <lb xml:id="p1-l14"/>de communiquer ma <rs>lettre<ref type="letter" target="K_5747"/></rs> à la
      <lb xml:id="p1-l15"/>Direction.
      </p>
    </body><back>
      <div type="closer">
        <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_6142_p5"><lb xml:id="p1-l16"/>Agréez mes salutations les
<lb xml:id="p1-l17"/>plus empressées</p>
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_6142_p6"><lb xml:id="p1-l18"/>Votre devoué</p>
      </div>
      <div type="signature">
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_6142_p7"><lb xml:id="p1-l19"/>Maraini
</p>
      </div>
    </back></text></TEI>